      "title": "PHP JS Developer (m/f/d)",
      "description": "<p>We are looking for a talented PHP &amp; Javascript Developer (m/w/d) to work in a team to manage both our backend and frontend applications.</p>\n<p>For this position, we are looking for someone who has in-depth knowledge of object-oriented PHP programming, an understanding of MVC designs, S.O.L.I.D principles, Design patterns and working knowledge of front-end technologies including HTML5, JavaScript, and CSS3. In addition to that, some level of experience in frontend frameworks is a bonus.</p>\n<p>Responsibilites\nWrite “clean” and well-designed code\nProduce detailed specifications\nWrite functional requirement documents and guides\nTroubleshoot, test and maintain the core product software and databases to ensure strong optimization and functionality\nContribute in all phases of the development lifecycle\nFollow industry best practices\nDevelop and deploy new features to facilitate related procedures and tools if necessary\nUpdating and altering application features to enhance performance\nStay up-to-date on emerging technologies</p>\n<p>Requirements\nFluent English language skills\nDemonstrable knowledge of web technologies including HTML, CSS, Javascript, AJAX etc\nExperience with PHP frameworks such as Laravel or Symfony.\nIdeally software development experience in PHP and Javascript\nDesirable experience with Javascript frontend frameworks such as ReactJS, AngularJS and/or VueJS.\nGood knowledge of relational databases, version control tools and of developing web services\nPassion for best design and coding practices and a desire to develop new bold ideas\nBS/MS degree in Computer Science, Engineering or a related subject is advantageous</p>\n<p>Our Offer\nHigh level of responsibility and collaboration with a world-class team of international, diverse and experienced scientists, doctors, market specialists and software developers\nMinimal steps to decision making with quick access to senior management\nBeing part of a fast-paced, dynamic and internationally growing company</p>\n<p>Does this pique your interest?\nThen please submit your application, including CV, cover letter, salary expectations and your earliest possible start date. Your application will be handled with confidentiality.</p>\n",
