      "company": "Spotler Group",
      "company_url": "https://spotlergroup.com/",
      "location": "Utrecht",
      "title": "(Junior) PHP Developer (Full Stack)",
      "description": "<p><strong>Spotler Group, an Marketing software company with over 2500 clients in 8 European countries transmitting over 9 billion messages every year, is looking for a</strong></p>\n<p><strong>(Junior) PHP Developer (Full Stack)</strong>\n<strong>Fulltime – Utrecht</strong></p>\n<p>Are you that result-driven Junior PHP Developer who wants to work on a marketing automation platform of the largest Email Service Provider in the Netherlands? Do you want to work together with a team of developers for great organisations such as PostNL, Heineken and Ticketveiling.nl? Then Spotler group / Tripolis is looking for you!</p>\n<p><strong>What will you be doing?</strong>\nAs a PHP developer you are part of our dedicated development team. Together with the other developers you’ll be working on customer projects. In addition, you also work on the roadmap of our marketing automation platform.\nTripolis Enterprise is a complete SaaS marketing automation platform which enables our clients to create beautiful emails, landing pages and surveys. They send their communication quickly and securely to millions of recipients. Clients can send a one-time email or create a complete flow based on triggers.</p>\n<p><strong>Who are you?</strong>\nYou are a full stack developer (PHP, MySQL) who works in an Agile framework and is result driven.</p>\n<p>Furthermore, we ask:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>At least 1 year of experience with software development</li>\n<li>You have knowledge of PHP 7+</li>\n<li>You have knowledge of MySQL</li>\n<li>You have knowledge of HTML 5 and CSS</li>\n<li>You are familiar with React, JavaScript and Angular</li>\n<li>You are familiar with Test Driven Development</li>\n<li>You have knowledge of Git and Docker</li>\n<li>You have a positive ‘can-do’ attitude</li>\n<li>You have self-confidence and an eye for detail</li>\n<li>You are comfortable with working under pressure</li>\n<li>You are a real team player</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What do we offer in return?</strong>\nWe offer a position for 40 hours a week in a working environment where you are challenged to bring out the best in yourself every day. After all, our field is still developing. Grow with us in a company with international ambitions. You can work for us from home, but you can also work at one of our locations in Utrecht, Rotterdam or Zoetermeer.</p>\n<p>Furthermore, we offer you:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A competitive salary that matches your experience and attractive fringe benefits, such as full reimbursement of travel expenses, internet and telephone allowance and a pension scheme</li>\n<li>25 days of holiday (based on a 40-hour work week)</li>\n<li>Plenty of opportunities to develop yourself</li>\n<li>A pleasant and inspiring work environment for developing your skills</li>\n<li>The nicest colleagues to learn from and laugh with</li>\n</ul>\n",
      "how_to_apply": "<p>Apply today and become our new PHP Developer!\nSend us your CV and motivation via our <strong><a href=\"https://www.spotler.jobs/php-developer-full-stack/nl?utm_source=github&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_term=2021&amp;utm_content=184243&amp;utm_campaign=junior-php-developer-full-stack\">application form</a></strong></p>\n<p><strong>About Spotler Group / Tripolis</strong>\nDo you say marketing automation? Then you say Tripolis! We are experts in the delivery of personalised communication to consumers and organisations all over the world. Think for instance of the track &amp; trace email of your last order, an offer for an extension from your telephone provider or an SMS message to remind you of your dentist appointment. We make communication truly personal. Behind our products and services lies a world of technology that is becoming more dynamic every day. Large organisations such as PostNL, Heineken, ANWB, ABN AMRO, Essent, Ticketveiling.nl and Wageningen University &amp; Research rely on our technology and people every day to send millions of messages a day.\nTripolis is part of the largest Email Service Provider (ESP) of the Netherlands: Spotler Group. Spotler Group has more than 2,500 customers in 8 European countries who send more than 9 billion messages per year.</p>\n",
      "company_logo": "https://jobs.github.com/rails/active_storage/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBbHFnIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--cd9fb74541eb627123af0b7564e0e9e06259dcf0/Logo%20Spotler%20group.png"
